============================================================

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   ATP
Formula: ADP + Pi → ATP
Note:    Universal energy currency of all living cells

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Planck's Constant
Formula: h = 6.626×10⁻³⁴ J·s
Note:    Quantum of action; E = hf for photon energy

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Photosynthesis
Formula: 6CO₂+6H₂O+light→C₆H₁₂O₆+6O₂
Note:    How plants produce energy from sunlight

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Pi
Formula: π ≈ 3.14159265358979...
Note:    Ratio of circle circumference to diameter

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Gravitational Force
Formula: F = Gm1m2/r²
Note:    Universal gravitation between all masses

============================================================
  MATHEMATICS
============================================================

Theorem/Law:  Euler's Identity
Branch:       Complex Analysis
Formula:      e^(iπ) + 1 = 0
Applications: Signal processing, quantum mechanics
Discoverer:   Leonhard Euler (1748)

Theorem/Law:  Central Limit Theorem
Branch:       Statistics
Formula:      Sample means approach normal distribution
Applications: Polling, quality control, finance
Discoverer:   Lyapunov (1901)

Theorem/Law:  Binomial Theorem
Branch:       Algebra
Formula:      (a+b)^n = sum of C(n,k) a^k b^(n-k)
Applications: Probability, statistics, polynomial algebra
Discoverer:   Newton/Pascal (1665)

